></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打飛段既智戰超好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />諗極都諗唔到不死二人組會點死<br />\n追連載果時睇好熱血"},{"pid":"5292458afc4afd56f575c9731e3f46663cbf3121","tid":248561,"uid":115988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T05:16:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n路人甲look <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一出場中忍試就扮學長，又r 第七班做frd好噁心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知第二次出場，係醫院扮暗部搶佐助，就吹到同卡卡西差唔多實力，公平咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />明明到左後期打六道卡卡西實力仲係木葉村中上<br />\n<br />\n好喇轉個頭大蛇丸殘廢，兜竟然可以單挑鳴人+靜音+鋼手 都夠做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要將醫療忍術用到出神入化切斷神經，鋼手都嚇一跳<br />\n<br />\n大蛇丸死左，兜將佢d細胞移植係自己個身，死唔斷氣咁係木葉搞搞震擦存在感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後忍界大戰，復活+威脅斑不自量力，同鼬打果時睇到兜幾咁自大，係出自佢幾咁自卑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兜不知幾正<br />\n同大蛇丸、班 都係有魅力角色<br />\n相反死忠鐘意嘅自來也、鼬太知，我就完全唔鐘意</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大蛇丸又一煩膠<br />\n一早死左，佐鼬大戰時係佐助個肚彈出黎，出場一秒再死多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑到肚痛<br />\n<br />\n講起佐鼬大戰，<br />\n鼬最後打到佐助無還擊之力，第一次睇以為鼬奸笑咁伸隻手去挖佐助隻眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n後來先知原來係微笑走去佐助面對彈佢額頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對不起哥哥又陪不到你，這是最後一次了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d106a3356e800c546e0e84eed7e14f4c4c1e1a07","tid":248561,"uid":58076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T06:12:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n路人甲look <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n